What is your overall goal? To be able to read all the SNES buttons on the NES, or have a game already written for two controllers to work with one? If you just want to read it, you can just hook it to one controller port and read more bits. The NES will read all buttons on a SNES controller just fine.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Wed Jul 14, 2010 12:38 pm</p><hr />
